Advanced Animal Care of Colorado

1530 Riverside Avenue Fort Collins, CO 80524 (970) 493-3333 (970) 315-3545 (Fax) hospital@advancedanimalcareofcolorado.com http://advancedanimalcareofcolorado.vetstreet.com/

AACC is a full service Fort Collins veterinary hospital providing small animal care. Our Dog Tales Activity Center offer dog grooming, training, daycare & dog boarding in Fort Collins. Stop by today!

SERVICES: Agility Classes, Behavioral Medicine, Dental Care Diagnostic Imaging, Doggie Day Care, General Practice Care, Grooming, Hospice and Euthanasia Services, House Calls, Lodging, Microchipping, Nutritional Counseling, Obedience Classes, Pain Management, Parasite Prevention and Control, Puppy and Kitten Care, Reproduction Medicine, Senior Care, Surgery, Swimming

BUSINESS HOURS: Monday - Friday ; 7:00 am - 7:00 pm Saturday: 7:00 am - 4:00 pm
